data.description: GREAT OPPORTUNITY  Bring the family to this six bedroom three bath home. Large backyard for dogs or entertainment.  Large Porcelain tile floors and Granite counter tops along with stainless steel appliances. The open floor plan allows you to entertain guests from multiple areas of the home. . The Second floor offers a bonus room at the top of the stairs and a total of six bedrooms. This home is located near I75 in the Riverbend West subdivision. It boasts a resort style pool and plenty of park space.  COME SEE FOR YOUR SELF
